    name (i.e. stash@{%d}) so that the stash diff updates correctly after
    calling `git stash drop $stash`. The issue can be reproduced by deleting
    one of the first N-1 stash and pressing Enter after the reload. The bug
    is caused by the commit->id, which are used in determining whether to
    refresh the diff view or not, does not change when the modified stash
    list is reloaded.

