    a7eb3057ec70d4948ca5f2de98fcf29d844085b4) which passed the terminal
    width to git-diff using `--stat=%(width)`. This feature was introduced
    in Git version 1.7.10 released 2013-04-06 and causes problems for older
    versions of Git.
    
